  "original_title": "\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0b86\u0b9a\u0ba9\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0b9c\u0bbf\u0bb0 : \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Vajira for Ranil's Parliamentary seat: Gazette published",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "A gazette notification has been issued appointing Vajira Abeywardena of the United National Party to the vacant National List Member of Parliament seat due to the election of Ranil Wickremesinghe as President.",
        "While the name of Ruvan Vijayavardhana was also nominated to fill the national list member of the United National Party, Vajira Abeywardana, who served as the party's Galle District Member of Parliament, failed in the last general election, but now he has been selected in the national list."
      ],
